### Step 1: SpaceNodeMigrationQueryManager 接口新增方法

In `SpaceNodeMigrationQueryManager.java`, after `getMigrationTaskInfo`, add:

```java
    /**
     * 查询批量迁移任务进度
     */
    BatchMigrationTaskVo getBatchMigrationTaskInfo(String batchId);
```

Add import:
```java
import com.yottastudios.ns.collabspace.workspace.vo.BatchMigrationTaskVo;
```

### Step 2: SpaceNodeMigrationQueryManagerImpl 实现

In `SpaceNodeMigrationQueryManagerImpl.java`:

First, inject ISpaceService if not already injected. Add in the @Resource declarations:
```java
    @Resource
    private com.yottastudios.ns.collabspace.space.service.ISpaceService spaceService;
```

Then add method after `getMigrationTaskInfo`:

```java
    @Override
    public BatchMigrationTaskVo getBatchMigrationTaskInfo(String batchId) {
        List<SpaceNodeMigrationTaskEntity> tasks = spaceNodeMigrationTaskService.listByBatchId(batchId);
        if (tasks.isEmpty()) {
            return BatchMigrationTaskVo.builder().batchId(batchId).tasks(List.of()).build();
        }

        List<BatchMigrationSubTaskVo> subTasks = tasks.stream().map(task -> {
            String spaceName = "";
            try {
                com.yottastudios.ns.collabspace.space.entity.SpaceEntity space = spaceService.getBySpaceId(task.getSourceSpaceId());
                if (space != null) {
                    spaceName = space.getName();
                }
            } catch (Exception e) {
                log.warn("Failed to get space name for spaceId={}", task.getSourceSpaceId());
            }
            return new BatchMigrationSubTaskVo(task, spaceName);
        }).toList();

        return BatchMigrationTaskVo.builder().batchId(batchId).tasks(subTasks).build();
    }
```

